name: Alphaeus Information Technology
overview:
For the past 10 years, we have been Software Technology Management Consultants to small-to-medium enterprises (SMEs). Businesses also rely on Alphaeus Information Technology (ALIT.us) for software application development, training and maintenance, as well as implementation of open source technologies.

We advise senior management on Information Technology strategy, design of enterprise applications, and implementation of company-wide solutions.

Through innovative software design, we have turned data into mission-critical information through online custom-database web applications.
